title: Vattenfall - Silver Sponsor of PyCon DE & PyData
---
full_description: Vattenfall is a leading European energy company working for fossil freedom. The company develops and operates renewable energy sources, modern energy infrastructure, and digital solutions that support the transition to a sustainable energy system. With the help of data, AI, and modern technology, Vattenfall is building smarter and more reliable energy solutions for millions of customers. Open-source and Python play a key role in enabling collaboration, innovation, and scalable data-driven solutions across the company.

